Hygiene Auditor & Quality Control Officer
Responsibilities
Responsibilities:• To apply hygiene systems at Stores in assigned Region.• To deliver safety systems in products handling for Stores personnels.• To achieve hygiene standard at Stores.• Willing to be placed in Surabaya or Makassar.Requirements:• Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree  in Agriculture/Aquaculture/Forestry, Biology, Food Technology/Nutrition or equivalent.• Required skill(s): Food Safety, Hygiene Audit.• At least 3 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.• Preferably Supervisor / Coordinators specializing in Quality Control/Assurance or equivalent. Job role in Quality Control/Assurance or equivalent.• Has training skills, details oriented and good conceptual thinking.• Dynamic individual, flexible and able to take mobile tasks.• 3 Full-Time position(s) available.Please send your complete resume to: human_resources@transretail.co.id
